## 🚀 Getting Started

### Prerequisites
- A web browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge)
- A code editor (VS Code, Sublime Text, etc.)

### Installation

1. Clone the repository:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/amazon-replica.git
cd amazon-replica
```

2. Open the file in your browser:
   - Double-click `index.html`, or
   - Use a live server extension in your code editor

### Using Live Server (VS Code)
1. Install the "Live Server" extension
2. Right-click on `index.html` and select "Open with Live Server"

## 🎨 Design Features

### Color Scheme
- **Primary Dark**: `#131921` (Header/Footer)
- **Accent Orange**: `#ff9900` (Buttons, highlights)
- **Light Background**: `#f5f5f5` (Page background)
- **Text Dark**: `#111` (Primary text)

### Key Components

#### Header
- Logo branding
