## 💡 Customization

### Change Colors
Edit the CSS variables in the `<style>` section:
```css
background-color: #131921; /* Change header color */
background-color: #ff9900; /* Change accent color */
```

### Add More Products
Duplicate a product card in the products grid and update:
```html
<div class="product-card">
    <div class="product-image">📱</div>
    <div class="product-info">
        <div class="product-name">Your Product Name</div>
        <div class="product-rating">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ (123)</div>
        <div class="product-price">$99.99</div>
        <button class="add-to-cart-btn">Add to Cart</button>
    </div>
</div>
```

### Modify Category Icons
Change the emoji or add real images:
```html
<div class="category-icon">📱</div> <!-- Change this emoji -->
```

